snippet.title: Andrey Lebrov
snippet.description:
Head of CG & VFX @ Out of Nothing Ltd.

I'm a self-taught CG Artist. This fact is important as it is directly affecting the way I explain things. If some topics in CG or Cinematography world were intimidating or complicated for you before, It's quite likely to change on this channel. I've been there, I was looking for technical answers myself, and I found them. Now I would like to share my discoveries with you.

If you're on a journey of mastering CG & VFX - Welcome to the club. Click it.

For more interesting info go to my website: www.lebrov.com
